{"title":"Agent = Model + Harness","uid":"50a44c21c5ace093c2e46dadf7541f1f","slug":"Agent = Model + Harness","date":"2026-07-06T14:09:53.000Z","updated":"2026-07-06T14:09:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Agent = Model + Harness.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/agent.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Agent-x3D-Model-Harness：智能体的工程化定义\"><a href=\"#Agent-x3D-Model-Harness：智能体的工程化定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Agent &#x3D; Model + Harness：智能体的工程化定义\"></a>Agent &#x3D; Model + Harness：智能体的工程化定义</h1><h2 id=\"一、核心公式解读\"><a href=\"#一、核心公式解读\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、核心公式解读\"></a>一、核心公式解读</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Agent &#x3D; Model + Harness</code></pre>\n\n<p>这个简洁的公式揭示了现代AI智能体（Agent）的本质架构：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>组件</th>\n<th>含义</th>\n<th>类比</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Model</strong></td>\n<td>底层大语言模型（LLM）</td>\n<td>大脑</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Harness</strong></td>\n<td>外围工具系统与编排框架</td>\n<td>身体+工具箱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"二、Model：智能的核心引擎\"><a href=\"#二、Model：智能的核心引擎\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、Model：智能的核心引擎\"></a>二、Model：智能的核心引擎</h2><h3 id=\"2-1-基础能力\"><a href=\"#2-1-基础能力\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 基础能力\"></a>2.1 基础能力</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>推理能力</strong>：逻辑分析、规划决策</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>知识储备</strong>：预训练积累的世界知识</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>语言理解</strong>：自然语言交互的基石</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>上下文记忆</strong>：维持对话连贯性</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-2-关键特性\"><a href=\"#2-2-关键特性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 关键特性\"></a>2.2 关键特性</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># 示例：Model层关注的核心指标\nmodel_capabilities &#x3D; &#123;\n    &quot;context_window&quot;: &quot;128K tokens&quot;,\n    &quot;reasoning_depth&quot;: &quot;多步推理&quot;,\n    &quot;instruction_following&quot;: &quot;精确遵循指令&quot;,\n    &quot;tool_use_awareness&quot;: &quot;识别何时调用工具&quot;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"三、Harness：能力的扩展框架\"><a href=\"#三、Harness：能力的扩展框架\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、Harness：能力的扩展框架\"></a>三、Harness：能力的扩展框架</h2><p>Harness 是将 Model 从”聊天机器人”升级为”自主智能体”的关键基础设施。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-核心组件\"><a href=\"#3-1-核心组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.1 核心组件\"></a>3.1 核心组件</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Harness\n├── Tool System        # 工具系统\n│   ├── Function Calling\n│   ├── Code Interpreter\n│   └── External APIs\n├── Memory Management  # 记忆管理\n│   ├── Short-term Memory\n│   ├── Long-term Memory\n│   └── Retrieval Augmentation\n├── Planning Engine    # 规划引擎\n│   ├── Task Decomposition\n│   ├── ReAct Loop\n│   └── Reflection\n└── Safety Guardrails # 安全护栏\n    ├── Input Filtering\n    ├── Output Validation\n    └── Permission Control</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-2-关键技术实现\"><a href=\"#3-2-关键技术实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.2 关键技术实现\"></a>3.2 关键技术实现</h3><h4 id=\"Function-Calling（函数调用）\"><a href=\"#Function-Calling（函数调用）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Function Calling（函数调用）\"></a>Function Calling（函数调用）</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-json\" data-language=\"json\"><code class=\"language-json\">&#123;\n  &quot;type&quot;: &quot;function&quot;,\n  &quot;function&quot;: &#123;\n    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;search_web&quot;,\n    &quot;description&quot;: &quot;搜索互联网获取实时信息&quot;,\n    &quot;parameters&quot;: &#123;\n      &quot;query&quot;: &#123;&quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;&#125;,\n      &quot;max_results&quot;: &#123;&quot;type&quot;: &quot;integer&quot;, &quot;default&quot;: 5&#125;\n    &#125;\n  &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"ReAct-循环（Reasoning-Acting）\"><a href=\"#ReAct-循环（Reasoning-Acting）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ReAct 循环（Reasoning + Acting）\"></a>ReAct 循环（Reasoning + Acting）</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Thought: 用户想查询天气，我需要调用天气API\nAction: call_api(&quot;weather&quot;, city&#x3D;&quot;福州&quot;)\nObservation: 返回&quot;晴，28°C&quot;\nThought: 信息完整，可以回复用户\nFinal Answer: 福州今天晴天，气温28°C</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"RAG（检索增强生成）\"><a href=\"#RAG（检索增强生成）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"RAG（检索增强生成）\"></a>RAG（检索增强生成）</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">User Query → Embedding → Vector DB Search \n         ↓\nRelevant Documents Retrieved\n         ↓\nContext + Query → LLM → Final Response</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"四、不同Harness框架对比\"><a href=\"#四、不同Harness框架对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、不同Harness框架对比\"></a>四、不同Harness框架对比</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>框架</th>\n<th>特点</th>\n<th>适用场景</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>LangChain</strong></td>\n<td>生态丰富，组件化</td>\n<td>快速原型开发</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>AutoGPT</strong></td>\n<td>自主任务执行</td>\n<td>复杂多步骤任务</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Semantic Kernel</strong></td>\n<td>微软出品，企业级</td>\n<td>.NET&#x2F;Azure生态</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>CrewAI</strong></td>\n<td>多Agent协作</td>\n<td>团队式任务分配</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Dify</strong></td>\n<td>可视化编排</td>\n<td>低代码应用搭建</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Coze</strong></td>\n<td>字节跳动，插件丰富</td>\n<td>社交&#x2F;内容创作</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"五、实战案例：一个完整的Agent\"><a href=\"#五、实战案例：一个完整的Agent\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、实战案例：一个完整的Agent\"></a>五、实战案例：一个完整的Agent</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># 简化的Agent实现示例\nclass SimpleAgent:\n    def __init__(self, model, tools):\n        self.model &#x3D; model          # 大脑\n        self.tools &#x3D; tools          # 工具集\n        self.memory &#x3D; []            # 短期记忆\n        self.max_steps &#x3D; 10         # 最大推理步数\n    \n    def run(self, user_input):\n        # 1. 添加用户输入到记忆\n        self.memory.append(f&quot;User: &#123;user_input&#125;&quot;)\n        \n        for step in range(self.max_steps):\n            # 2. 构建提示词（包含记忆和可用工具）\n            prompt &#x3D; self.build_prompt()\n            \n            # 3. Model推理\n            response &#x3D; self.model.generate(prompt)\n            \n            # 4. 解析响应，判断是否需要调用工具\n            action &#x3D; self.parse_action(response)\n            \n            if action[&quot;type&quot;] &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;final_answer&quot;:\n                return action[&quot;content&quot;]\n            \n            elif action[&quot;type&quot;] &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;tool_call&quot;:\n                # 5. Harness执行工具调用\n                result &#x3D; self.execute_tool(action)\n                \n                # 6. 将结果反馈给Model\n                self.memory.append(f&quot;Tool Result: &#123;result&#125;&quot;)\n        \n        return &quot;Max steps reached.&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"六、设计原则与最佳实践\"><a href=\"#六、设计原则与最佳实践\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、设计原则与最佳实践\"></a>六、设计原则与最佳实践</h2><h3 id=\"6-1-模型选择策略\"><a href=\"#6-1-模型选择策略\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.1 模型选择策略\"></a>6.1 模型选择策略</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>任务复杂度</strong>：简单任务选轻量模型，复杂推理选强大模型</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>成本考量</strong>：平衡性能与API调用成本</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>延迟敏感度</strong>：实时场景需要更快的推理速度</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"6-2-Harness设计要点\"><a href=\"#6-2-Harness设计要点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.2 Harness设计要点\"></a>6.2 Harness设计要点</h3><ol>\n<li><p><strong>松耦合</strong>：Model与Tools解耦，便于替换升级</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>可观测性</strong>：记录每一步的推理过程和工具调用</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>容错机制</strong>：工具调用失败时的优雅降级</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>权限控制</strong>：敏感操作需用户确认</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"6-3-常见陷阱\"><a href=\"#6-3-常见陷阱\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.3 常见陷阱\"></a>6.3 常见陷阱</h3><p>   ❌ 过度依赖模型记忆，忽略RAG<br>   ❌ 工具描述模糊，导致模型误用<br>   ❌ 缺乏循环终止条件，陷入死循环<br>   ❌ 忽略安全验证，产生有害输出</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"七、未来演进方向\"><a href=\"#七、未来演进方向\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、未来演进方向\"></a>七、未来演进方向</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Agent 1.0: Model + Basic Harness\n     ↓\nAgent 2.0: Multi-Model + Advanced Harness\n     ↓\nAgent 3.0: Self-Improving Agents\n     ↓\nAgent 4.0: Collaborative Agent Networks</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"关键技术趋势\"><a href=\"#关键技术趋势\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关键技术趋势\"></a>关键技术趋势</h3><ul>\n<li><p><strong>MoE（混合专家）</strong>：动态路由到最合适的子模型</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Tool Learning</strong>：模型自主学习新工具的使用</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Multi-Agent</strong>：多个Agent分工协作完成复杂任务</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>持续学习</strong>：通过反馈不断优化行为策略</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"八、总结\"><a href=\"#八、总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八、总结\"></a>八、总结</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">Agent &#x3D; Model (认知能力) + Harness (行动能力)\n\nModel 决定了智能的上限\nHarness 决定了能力的边界\n\n好的Agent &#x3D; 强大的Model + 精心设计的Harness</code></pre>\n\n<p>这个公式提醒我们：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>不要只关注模型参数</strong>，Harness的设计同样关键</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>工具即能力</strong>，每增加一个高质量工具，Agent就多一项技能</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>系统工程思维</strong>比单纯的模型调优更重要</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":false,"text":"AI 智能体的工程化架构解析，从 Model + Harness 公式理解 Agent 的本质与实现...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.1k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编程","slug":"编程","count":27,"path":"api/categories/编程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"AI Agent","slug":"AI-Agent","count":2,"path":"api/tags/AI-Agent.json"},{"name":"LLM","slug":"LLM","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LLM.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Agent-x3D-Model-Harness%EF%BC%9A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8C%96%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Agent &#x3D; Model + Harness：智能体的工程化定义</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、核心公式解读</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81Model%EF%BC%9A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、Model：智能的核心引擎</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-1-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.1 基础能力</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-2-%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.2 关键特性</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81Harness%EF%BC%9A%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三、Harness：能力的扩展框架</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-1-%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.1 核心组件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-2-%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.2 关键技术实现</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Function-Calling%EF%BC%88%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Function Calling（函数调用）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ReAct-%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%88Reasoning-Acting%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ReAct 循环（Reasoning + Acting）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#RAG%EF%BC%88%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">RAG（检索增强生成）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8CHarness%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94\"><span class=\"toc-text\">四、不同Harness框架对比</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84Agent\"><span class=\"toc-text\">五、实战案例：一个完整的Agent</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-lev